The guarantee to discover an optimal subgroup in purely numerical data is a useful task and we now motivate it for our ongoing research project. We are currently working on optimization methods for urban farms (e.g., AeroFarms, Infarm, FUL1). In that setting, plant growth recipes involve many numerical attributes (temperature, hydrometry, CO\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
